\c 14
\s Jehovha achabata ushe hwose
\p
\v 1 Tarirai, zuva raJehovha rinosvika, nenguva iyo zvawakapamba zvichagoverwa mukati mako.
\v 2 Nokuti ndichaunganidza ndudzi dzose dzavanhu kuzorwa neJerusaremu; guta richakundwa, dzimba dzichapambwa, navakadzi vavo vachachinyiwa; hafu yeguta vachatapwa, asi vakasara vavanhu havangabviswi muguta.
\v 3 Ipapo Jehovha achabuda, ndokurwa nendudzi idzedzo, sezvaakarwa nezuva rehondo.
\v 4 Nezuva iro tsoka dzake dzichamira pagomo reMiorivhi, riri pamberi peJerusaremu kurutivi rwamabvazuva; gomo reMiorivhi richapamuka napakati, zvichibva kumabvazuva zvichienda kumavirazuva, kukavapo mupata mukuru kwazvo; imwe hafu yegomo ichatsedukira kurutivi rwokumusoro, imwe hafu yaro kurutivi rwezasi.
\v 5 Muchatiza nomumupata wamakomo angu, nokuti mupata wamakomo uchandosvika paAzeri; zvirokwazvo muchatiza, sezvamakatiza kudengenyeka kwenyika pamazuva aUziya mambo waJudha; ipapo Jehovha Mwari wenyu achauya, navatsvene vose pamwechete newe.
\p
\v 6 Zvino nezuva iro chiedza chichashaikwa, zvinopenya zvichadzimwa.
\v 7 Asi richava zuva rimwe rinozikamwa naJehovha, hapangavi namasikati kana husiku, asi nenguva yamadekwana chiedza chichavapo.
\p
\v 8 Zvino nezuva iro mvura mhenyu zhinji ichabuda muJerusaremu; imwe hafu yayo ichayerera kugungwa rokumabvazuva, imwe hafu yayo kugungwa rokumavirazuva; zvichaitwa pamunakamwe napachando.
\v 9 Jehovha achava Mambo wenyika yose; nezuva iro Jehovha achava mumwechete, nezita rake rimwechete.
\p
\v 10 Nyika yose ichaita sebani, zvichibva Gebha kusvikira paRimoni, kurutivi rwezasi rweJerusaremu; iro richakwiridzwa, richagara panzvimbo yaro, kubva pasuo raBhenjamini kusvikira kunzvimbo yesuo rokutanga, kusvikira kusuo rekona, nokubva kurutura rwaHananeri kusvikira kuzvishiro zvewaini zvamambo.
\v 11 Vanhu vachagaramo; kutukwa hakungazovipo, asi Jerusaremu richagara rakachengetwa.
\p
\v 12 Uku ndiko kurova Jehovha kwaacharova nako ndudzi dzose dzavanhu vakarwa neJerusaremu, nyama yavo ichaora vamire namakumbo avo, meso avo achaorera mumakomba awo, norurimi rwavo ruchaorera mumiromo yavo.
\p
\v 13 Zvino nezuva iro kunyonganiswa kukuru kunobva kuna Jehovha kuchavapo pakati pavo; mumwe nomumwe achabata ruoko rwowokwake, uye ruoko rwake ruchasimudzirwa ruoko rwowokwake.
\v 14 Judha vacharwawo paJerusaremu; fuma yendudzi dzose dzavanhu vakapoteredza ichaunganidzwa, inoti ndarama, nesirivha, nenguo, zvizhinji kwazvo.
\v 15 Sezvakaita kurohwa uku, ndizvo zvichaitawo kurohwa kwamabhiza namahesera, nengamera, nembongoro, nezvipfuwo zvose zvichavapo pamisasa iyo.
\p
\v 16 Zvino vose vakasara vendudzi dzose dzakarwa neJerusaremu, vachakwira gore rimwe nerimwe kundonamata Mambo, iye Jehovha wehondo, nokutamba mutambo wamatumba.
\v 17 Ani naani pamarudzi enyika asingakwiri Jerusaremu kundonamata Mambo, Jehovha wehondo, haanganisirwi mvura.
\v 18 Kana rudzi rwavaljipiti rusingakwiri, vakasasvikapo, naivo vachavingwa nokurohwa Jehovha kwaacharova nako ndudzi dzavanhu dzinoramba kukwira kundotamba mutambo wamatumba.
\v 19 Uku ndiko kurohwa kwavaEgipita nokurohwa kwendudzi dzose dzinoramba kukwira kundotamba mutambo wamatumba.
\p
\v 20 Nezuva iro pamatare anorira amabhiza pachanyorwa, pachiti, ZVITSVENE KUNA JEHOVHA; nehari dziri mumba maJehovha dzichafanana nembiya dziri pamberi pearitari.
\v 21 Zvirokwazvo, hari imwe neimwe paJerusaremu napaJudha ichava tsvene kuna Jehovha wehondo; vose vanoda kubayira vachauya vachidzitora, kuzobikiramo; nezuva iro hapachazovi nomuKenani mumba maJehovha wehondo.
